#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.159"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.159:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.159:0.2"
msgid "16. Saddhammavagga"
msgstr "16. The True Teaching"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.159:0.3"
msgid "159. Udāyīsutta"
msgstr "159. With Udāyī"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.159:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​"
msgstr "So I have heard."

msgctxt "an5.159:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kosambiyaṃ viharati ghositārāme."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Kosambi, in Ghosita’s Monastery."

msgctxt "an5.159:1.3"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā udāyī mahatiyā gihiparisāya parivuto dhammaṃ "
"desento nisinno hoti."
msgstr ""
"Now, at that time Venerable Udāyī was sitting teaching Dhamma, surrounded by "
"a large assembly of laypeople."

msgctxt "an5.159:1.4"
msgid ""
"Addasā kho āyasmā ānando āyasmantaṃ udāyiṃ mahatiyā gihiparisāya parivutaṃ "
"dhammaṃ desentaṃ nisinnaṃ."
msgstr "Seeing this, Venerable Ānanda"

msgctxt "an5.159:1.5"
msgid ""
"Disvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā "
"ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā ānando bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and said to him:"

#. VAR: desento nisinnoti
msgctxt "an5.159:1.6"
msgid ""
"“āyasmā, bhante, udāyī mahatiyā gihiparisāya parivuto dhammaṃ desetī”ti."
msgstr ""
"“Sir, Venerable Udāyī is teaching Dhamma, surrounded by a large assembly of "
"laypeople.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an5.159:2.1"
msgid "“Na kho, ānanda, sukaraṃ paresaṃ dhammaṃ desetuṃ."
msgstr "“Ānanda, it’s not easy to teach Dhamma to others."

msgctxt "an5.159:2.2"
msgid ""
"Paresaṃ, ānanda, dhammaṃ desentena pañca dhamme ajjhattaṃ upaṭṭhāpetvā "
"paresaṃ dhammo desetabbo."
msgstr ""
"You should establish five things in yourself before teaching Dhamma to "
"others."

msgctxt "an5.159:2.3"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

#. VAR: Anupubbiṃ kathaṃ → ānupubbikathaṃ (bj) | anupubbikathaṃ (s1-3, pts1, mr)
msgctxt "an5.159:2.4"
msgid "‘Anupubbiṃ kathaṃ kathessāmī’ti paresaṃ dhammo desetabbo;"
msgstr ""
"You should teach Dhamma to others thinking: ‘I will teach step by step.’ …"

msgctxt "an5.159:2.5"
msgid "‘pariyāyadassāvī kathaṃ kathessāmī’ti paresaṃ dhammo desetabbo;"
msgstr "‘I will talk explaining my methods.’ …"

msgctxt "an5.159:2.6"
msgid "‘anuddayataṃ paṭicca kathaṃ kathessāmī’ti paresaṃ dhammo desetabbo;"
msgstr "‘I will talk out of kindness.’ …"

msgctxt "an5.159:2.7"
msgid "‘na āmisantaro kathaṃ kathessāmī’ti paresaṃ dhammo desetabbo;"
msgstr "‘I will not talk while secretly hoping to profit.’ …"

msgctxt "an5.159:2.8"
msgid ""
"‘attānañca parañca anupahacca kathaṃ kathessāmī’ti paresaṃ dhammo desetabbo."
msgstr "‘I will talk without hurting myself or others.’"

msgctxt "an5.159:2.9"
msgid "Na kho, ānanda, sukaraṃ paresaṃ dhammaṃ desetuṃ."
msgstr "It’s not easy to teach Dhamma to others."

msgctxt "an5.159:2.10"
msgid ""
"Paresaṃ, ānanda, dhammaṃ desentena ime pañca dhamme ajjhattaṃ upaṭṭhāpetvā "
"paresaṃ dhammo desetabbo”ti."
msgstr ""
"You should establish these five things in yourself before teaching Dhamma to "
"others.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.159:2.11"
msgid "Navamaṃ."
msgstr ""
